entries.journal_entry_description: Inaldra needs your help to eliminate a particularly nasty Hutt boss on the lower level of the station.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Inaldra wants you to kill the Hutt Boss on the lower level. Take the elevator to the lower level to get to him.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to go to the Lower Level
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: In the lower level of the station, one of the hangars has been overrun by Hutt minions. Kill the boss and weaken them.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Kill the Hutt Boss in Cargo Bay 2
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You have removed the Hutt Boss from power. Use the elevator to return to the main level and talk to Inaldra.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to Return to the Main Level
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Head back to Inaldra and tell her that you killed the Hutt boss.
